Welcome to No.3 Craft Beer Bar!
21 and over—no exceptions.
Love your furry friends? So do we, but service animals only (tell your dog we’re sorry).
And yes, we’re proudly Veteran-Owned.
Which means we run a tight ship—good drinks, great vibes, and no nonsense.
Cheers!
About Us
At No.3 Craft Beer Bar, we’re all about the chill vibes and fantastic brews! With 20 rotating taps and an impressive selection of bottles and cans, there's always something new to sip on, whether you stay to enjoy or take it home. Join us for weekly Thursday night trivia or catch the excitement of our Wednesday dart league. Dive into a game of Golden Tee or shuffleboard, then unwind with friends during our monthly Paint & Sip events. Remember, while we don’t serve food, you’re welcome to bring your favorite takeout from nearby restaurants!
